metadata.name: Gangboy #10 - by Eddie Gangland
metadata.description: The Gangland collection is made up of original illustrations by Eddie Gangland.  Each illustration has been made into a unique 'GANG' token and maintained on the Ethereum blockchain.  The first character in the Gangland Universe is Gangboy.  This token is 1/300 unique tokens that will ever exist for the Gangboy character within this collection.  Each illustration is created by Eddie Gangland and completely original.
